ğŸ›  Development

Install dependencies:

npm install


Run the dev server:

npm run dev


The development preview should match what you see inside Lovable.

ğŸ§ª Build

To create a production build locally:

npm run build


Preview the production bundle:

npm run preview


This ensures the local build works before deploying to Cloudflare.

ğŸŒ Deployment (Cloudflare Pages)

The site is automatically deployed from the main branch via Cloudflare Pages.

